<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>KTU Portal</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: whitesmoke;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        header {
            background-color: darkblue;
            color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        nav {
            background-color: orange;
            padding: 10px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        nav a {
            color: black;
            margin: 0 15px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .container {
            padding: 20px;
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: auto;
        }

        .section {
            background-color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            border: 1px solid lightgrey;
        }

        h2 {
            color: darkblue;
            border-bottom: 2px solid orange;
        }

        .login-form {
            background-color: beige;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
        }

        input {
            width: 90%;
            padding: 10px;
            margin: 10px 0;
            font-family: Arial;
        }

        button {
            background-color: darkblue;
            color: white;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border: none;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-family: Arial;
        }

        .reg-link {
            display: block;
            background-color: whitesmoke;
            padding: 10px;
            margin: 5px 0;
            color: darkblue;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-left: 5px solid orange;
        }

        .reg-link:hover {
            background-color: lightgrey;
        }

        footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 30px 20px;
            background-color: black;
            color: white;
        }

        .footer-content {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: auto;
        }

        .social-links {
            margin: 15px 0;
        }

        .social-links a {
            color: orange;
            text-decoration: none;
            margin: 0 10px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .contact-info {
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            color: lightgrey;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <header>
        <h1>APJ Abdul Kalam Technological University</h1>
    </header>

    <nav>
        <a href="#">Home</a>
        <a href="#syllabus">Syllabus</a>
        <a href="#exams">Exam Registration</a>
        <a href="#login">Login</a>
        <a href="#about">About</a>
    </nav>

    <div class="container">
        
        <div id="login" class="section">
            <h2>Student Login</h2>
            <div class="login-form">
                <label>Register Number:</label><br>
                <input type="text" placeholder="Enter ID"><br>
                <label>Password:</label><br>
                <input type="password" placeholder="Enter Password"><br>
                <button>Login</button>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div id="exams" class="section">
            <h2>Exam Registration</h2>
            <p>Click the links below to apply for upcoming examinations:</p>
            <a href="#" class="reg-link">B.Tech S8 Regular Examination - April 2024</a>
            <a href="#" class="reg-link">B.Tech S1 & S2 Supplementary Examination - May 2024</a>
            <a href="#" class="reg-link">MBA T4 Regular/Supplementary Examination</a>
            <a href="#" class="reg-link">Ph.D. Coursework Examination Registration</a>
        </div>

        <div id="syllabus" class="section">
            <h2>Syllabus & Courses</h2>
            <ul>
                <li>Computer Science Engineering</li>
                <li>Mechanical Engineering</li>
                <li>Civil Engineering</li>
                <li>Electronics Engineering</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div id="announcements" class="section">
            <h2>Latest News</h2>
            <p><b>Results:</b> B.Tech S7 Results are out.</p>
            <p><b>Exam:</b> S8 Registration starts tomorrow.</p>
        </div>

        <div id="about" class="section">
            <h2>About the University</h2>
            <p>APJ Abdul Kalam Technological University (KTU) is a state government university located in Thiruvananthapuram, Kerala. Established in 2014, its primary mission is to coordinate and improve the standards of technical education in the state.</p>
            
            <p><b>Our Reach:</b> The university provides leadership to over 150 affiliated engineering colleges across Kerala, ensuring a unified curriculum and examination system for thousands of students.</p>
            
            <p><b>Academic Programs:</b> KTU offers a wide range of undergraduate, postgraduate, and doctoral programs, including B.Tech, M.Tech, MBA, MCA, and Ph.D. in various engineering and management disciplines.</p>
            
            <p><b>Key Objectives:</b></p>
            <ul>
                <li>Standardization of technical curriculum and evaluation.</li>
                <li>Promotion of industry-institute interaction.</li>
                <li>Encouraging research and development in emerging technologies.</li>
                <li>Implementing e-governance for transparent university administration.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

    </div>

    <footer>
        <div class="footer-content">
            <p>&copy; 2023 KTU University - Thiruvananthapuram</p>
            
            <div class="contact-info">
                <p>Email: support@ktu.edu.in | registrar@ktu.edu.in</p>
                <p>Phone: +91 471 2598122</p>
            </div>

            <div class="social-links">
                <a href="#">Instagram</a>
                <a href="#">Facebook</a>
                <a href="#">Twitter/X</a>
            </div>
            
            <p style="font-size: 0.8rem; opacity: 0.7;">CET Campus, Thiruvananthapuram, Kerala 695016</p>
        </div>
    </footer>

</body>
</html>
